  <p class="sec-body" id="distNote" style="margin-bottom:18px">Goa's two districts showcase the state's complete character. North Goa, bustling with activity and nightlife, and South Goa, serene with pristine beaches and untouched beauty. Both offer unique experiences, from cultural sites to natural wonders.</p>
